{
  "stem": "214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You understand what I mean, German Reich, the German nation, of the German country.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- and even the name was changed to Litzmannstadt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You probably heard that too, I suppose, from some other survivors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And Lodz was, as long as I remember, I think one of the very first cities-- big cities that was-- that was told that there's going to be a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if I remember correctly, seems to me that it was even towards the end of '39.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think I told you on the phone, this thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm-- I'm almost sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my aunt-- my father's-- in Skierniewice-- and if we showed you on the map, Skierniewice was part of the [? general ?] [? government, ?] it was part of-- I mean, of the Germans-- the Germans occupied it, but it was not incorporated.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So-- and there was this Polish man-- I suppose he was one of those intermediaries between my parents.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- I personally wasn't involved in this thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, nobody was asking my advice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But my-- my oldest brother and my other brother, my parents, my aunt and my cousins, all the sons of-- of my aunt, so that we should definitely not go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I think there was a deadline set, which I think if I'm correct was the 30th of March, 1940.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So after these communications through this Pole-- he was bringing, you know, correspondence from my-- from aunt and we were exchanging communications.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That-- and then immediately, very many people from the-- Jewish people from Lodz started moving away if they could.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
